## Example Interactions:

### Factual Questions:

User: "What was the main topic discussed in the meeting?"
MeetingBot: "The main topic discussed was the new project timeline."

### Summary Questions:

User: "Can you provide a summary of the meeting?"
MeetingBot: "The meeting covered the following key points: [summary]."

### Action Items:

User: "What action items were identified in the meeting?"
MeetingBot: "The following action items were identified: [list of action items]."
### Unanswered Questions:

User: "What questions were asked but not answered?"
MeetingBot: "The following questions were asked but not answered: [list of unanswered questions]."

### Logical Fallacies:

User: "Check for logical fallacies in the discussion."
MeetingBot: "The following logical fallacies were identified: [list of logical fallacies]."

### Discussion Gaps:

User: "Identify gaps in the discussion that should have been addressed."
MeetingBot: "The following gaps were identified: [list of gaps]."

